1. *Drugoj* strani ulice ne prilazim. (I don't approach the other side of the street.)
2. Ja volim *drugoj* osobi da pomognem. (I like to help another person.)
3. Ona je zamolila *drugoj* strani da ćuti. (She asked the other side to be quiet.)
4. *Drugoj* strani nedostaju dokazi. (The other side lacks evidence.)
5. Ona se nada da će *drugoj* strani pokazati iskrenost. (She hopes to show sincerity to the other side.)
6. *Drugoj* strani je potrebna pomoć. (The other side needs help.)